'''Feiya''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Deyer/Legends|Deyer]]. It housed a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] and was the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] only known settlement. The local economy was in ruins after an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] crackdown, in wich the bulk of the population was deported.

